title:
Effects of neutral $Z^{\prime}$ boson in $B_{s} \to \phi \ell^{+}
  \ell^{-}$ decay with polarized $\phi$ and the unpolarized and polarized $CP$
  violation asymmetry

abstract:
  In this paper, we give a constant $C$ in \cite[Theorem 1.2]{sha2014bounding}
by using an explicit Baker's inequality, hence we have an explicit bound of the
integral points on modular curves.
